# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CETRanker – Environment Variables
# 1. Go to https://app.supabase.com → Settings → API
# 2. Copy "Project URL" and "anon / public" key below
# 3. Rename this file to .env before running the app
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON=your-anon-public-key-here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google OAuth (optional — enables "Continue with Google")
# 1. Go to https://app.supabase.com → Authentication → Providers
# 2. Enable Google → paste your Google OAuth Client ID + Secret
# 3. No extra env vars needed here — Supabase handles the redirect
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
